# Documentation interne (garder seulement README.md, LICENSE.md, CONTRIBUTING.md)
*.md
!README.md
!LICENSE.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md

# Screenshots et fichiers temporaires
screenshots/
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
!assets/icons/*.png
